compareTo

public int compareTo(nu.xom.Attribute att)
compares attributes. As we cannot override Node.equals() which compares identity we have to compare components. order of sorting is: attribute class schemaType name name value null values of any component return -1

Parameters:
att - to compare
Returns:
0 if all content is identical, -1 if this less than att, 1 if greater value
